{{see|Pixel}}
==English==
===Etymology===
''[[pix]]'', pictures + ''[[element|el(ement)]]''; often taken to be a blend of “picture” and “element”, but this does not account for the ''x''.  First attested [[w:1969|1969]]

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪksəl|-ɪksəl]]

===Noun===
'''pixel''' (''plural'' '''pixels''')

#One of the tiny dots that make up the representation of an [[image]] in a [[computer]]'s [[memory]].

====Synonyms====
*[[pel]] (''rare'')

